      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Renderman Screenshot.jpeg\" width=\"1280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Screenshot.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542231407/Renderman%20Screenshot.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231419\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Renderman Screenshot.jpeg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542231407\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"989b12a1-782a-4fa4-9930-0283eec403c0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Screenshot.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Screenshot.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360 1x\"></span><p><br/>A camera model that approximates a number of real world physical effects. <br/><br/>This supports all of the traditional prman perspective camera settings including shaped motion blur and bokeh.</p><p>Some examples of the effects PxrCamera can do:</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Renderman Image 640x360 (2).jpeg\" width=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Image%20640x360%20(2).jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713311&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542231407/Renderman%20Image%20640x360%20(2).jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713311&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"360\" data-width=\"640\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231428\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Renderman Image 640x360 (2).jpeg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542231407\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d14648c3-1101-4ff0-94eb-0b7d1f88cc45\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Image%20640x360%20(2).jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713311&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Image%20640x360%20(2).jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713311&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Renderman Image 640x360 (1).jpeg\" width=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Image%20640x360%20(1).jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542231407/Renderman%20Image%20640x360%20(1).jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"360\" data-width=\"640\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231425\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Renderman Image 640x360 (1).jpeg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542231407\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f99bdd6d-b957-44e6-9433-46be1b3f58ab\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Image%20640x360%20(1).jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Image%20640x360%20(1).jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Renderman Image 640x360.jpeg\" width=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Image%20640x360.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542231407/Renderman%20Image%20640x360.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"360\" data-width=\"640\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231422\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Renderman Image 640x360.jpeg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542231407\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"cb14257e-465e-4a6f-a82a-9c60b32604ea\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Image%20640x360.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Image%20640x360.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Renderman Screenshot.jpeg\" width=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Screenshot.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542231407/Renderman%20Screenshot.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"360\" data-width=\"640\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231419\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Renderman Screenshot.jpeg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542231407\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"989b12a1-782a-4fa4-9930-0283eec403c0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Screenshot.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/Renderman%20Screenshot.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=360 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"final_image.jpeg\" width=\"1280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/final_image.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713311&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542231407/final_image.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713311&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231431\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"final_image.jpeg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542231407\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5e1fcfe6-e1a7-49e9-b0cc-702fb352a3b9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/final_image.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713311&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231407/final_image.jpeg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330713311&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720 1x\"></span><p /><p><br/><br/>Barrel Distortion / Chromatic Aberration / Split Diopter / Tilt-Shift / Vignetting<br/><br/><br/></p><hr/><h3 id=\"PxrCamera-StandardParameters\"><br/>Standard Parameters</h3><p><strong>fov</strong> </p><p>Field of view (FOV) in degrees. For rectangular images this is normally the FOV along the narrower image dimension.<br/><br/>Below is a conversion table for standard prime lenses to their horizontal fov value<br/><br/></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"d00f8a74-c96a-4bae-b660-0f991daab793\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong>lens mm</strong></p></th><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong>Horizontal fov</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>18mm</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>90</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>25</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>71.5</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>35mm</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>54.4</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>50mm</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>39.6</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>85mm</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>23.9</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>100mm</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>20.4</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>135mm</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>15.2</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><br/>Therefore, to mimick a 50mm prime lens with the PxrCamera, you would enter the value of 39.6 in the FOV parameter</p><p><strong>fov</strong> <strong>(end)</strong></p><p>Field of view (FOV) in degrees. Used to motion blur fast zooms. 0.0 means it is the same during the rendering</p><p><strong>F-stop</strong></p><p>Aperture size, controls depth of field blurriness. High values emulate a pinhole camera and depth of field is disabled.</p><p><strong>Focal Length</strong></p><p>The focal length of the camera in scene units measured from the camera lens. High F-stop values disable this.</p><p><strong>Focal Distance</strong></p><p>Distance to the focal plane where objects are in focus, measured in scene units from the camera to the object. High F-stop values disable this.<br/><br/></p><hr/><ul class=\"childpages-macro conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"adccbd16-665f-4af8-a1ef-b182aa90d856\" data-macro-id=\"50128d95-0495-41b2-9cc1-4386b84e78c7\" data-macro-name=\"children\"><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542231487/Aperture\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231487\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Aperture</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542231583/Tilt-Shift\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231583\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Tilt-Shift</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542231607/Lens+Distortion\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231607\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Lens Distortion</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542231686/DOF+Distortion\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231686\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">DOF Distortion</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542231710/Split+Diopter\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231710\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Split Diopter</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542231739/Chromatic+Aberration\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231739\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Chromatic Aberration</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542231763/Vignetting\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231763\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Vignetting</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542231817/Camera+Shutter\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231817\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Camera Shutter</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542231837/PxrCamera+Advanced\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231837\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrCamera Advanced</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542231854/Enhance\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231854\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Enhance</a></li></ul><p><br/><br/></p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
